{"tid":53143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先搞掂咗樓下條一放假就播歌嘅仆街","createTime":"2016-12-24T13:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T13:45:42.000Z","uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef044dcc9ab403c2a3cd84968357005cada4549","tid":53143,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"終於搵得佢耐，久唔久就係到播，最撚仆街喺用嗰d低音喇叭，關晒窗都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上個禮拜五六日變本加厲，由夜晚十二點開始一路播到朝早五六點<br />\n晚晚三點幾成個傻仔咁一路去樓上樓下搵係邊條仆街播歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱八點幾又開始播到勁撚大聲，忍唔住行去對落一層嘅單位，一行到去，隔住道門都聽撚到佢係到播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再有下次就係部lift到貼張紙，等佢隔離啲人都知佢嘅惡行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0393e35a6163fe5ce4768ed2f2ab05fcfe819b","tid":53143,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"fac63602144fba3fc64b6745e0a64fc3acd863f8","tid":53143,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"真係好撚自私，同嗰啲鍾意用iphone耳機聽歌開到勁撚大聲，又唔知自己對耳機漏聲漏到仆街要陪佢一齊聽嘅人一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7225c7bb94226c0674ae94a539087a90ae85a951","tid":53143,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"而家耳根清靜晒好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5000739d3dc8ed1f54f4f25d9fc5d254e2bafe","tid":53143,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"對唔住囉"}]}